snippet.title: Kādomon: Hyper Auto Battlers - Early Access Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Kādomon releases on March 25th on Steam! Wishlist Kādomon here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2125540/Kdomon_Hyper_Auto_Battlers/

Collect and battle over 180 unique creatures in this roguelike auto-battler. Level-up and evolve your Kādomon as you assemble the ultimate team, creating awesome synergies to beat BIG bosses!
